DESCRIPTION: Create and manage a backup of your server or your emojis
EXAMPLE:
{{prefix}}backup emoji create **- to create a backup of the emojis on the server**
{{prefix}}backup emoji delete Cg267T **- to delete the backup**
{{prefix}}backup server load Cg267T** - to load the backup**
{{prefix}}backup server create ** - to create a server backup**
{{prefix}}backup emoji list ** - to see the list of backups**
